    "introduction": "Ed Lilly is a British film director and screenwriter. His debut feature film, VS. (BBC Films), world premiered at the 2018 London Film Festival and was subsequently released theatrically before being bought by Netflix. Ed picked up a Writers' Guild nomination for \"Best Debut Screenplay\" and was long-listed in the British Independent Film Awards \"Debut Director\" and \"Debut Screenwriter\" categories. Ed is also a former Screen International \"Star of Tomorrow\" who has also directed on a number of high-end TV shows.",
